text.section:
In contracts with providers or in the provider manual or other document that sets forth the procedures for filing claims, an insurer shall disclose to providers:
The mailing or electronic address where claims should be sent for processing;
The phone number a provider may call to have questions and concerns regarding claims addressed;
Any entity to which the insurer has delegated claims payment functions; and
The address of any separate claims processing centers for specific types of services.
